@startuml green-bar-patterns

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontSize 14

title Green Bar Patterns — How to Make RED → GREEN

start

:Test is 🔴 RED;

if (Confident in\nthe implementation?) then (yes)

  :Use **Obvious Implementation**\nWrite the real code directly;
  :Run test;

  if (Surprised by RED?) then (yes)
    :Slow down!\nFall back to Fake It;
    detach
  else (no — ✅ GREEN)
  endif

else (no — unsure)

  :Use **Fake It**\nReturn a constant;
  :Run test → ✅ GREEN;

  :Add a **second test**\n(different input);
  :Run test → 🔴 RED;

  :Use **Triangulate**\nGeneralize from\ntwo examples;
  :Run both tests → ✅ GREEN;

endif

:Proceed to ♻️ REFACTOR;
stop

@enduml
